	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Wanted to clear something up.  Buffs like SLW and <BR>
Alacrity do stack with this item.  I believe even<BR>
the effect on Mith 2H and Exe Axe stack with both<BR>
of the above as well.  There is, however, a hard cap<BR>
on how low someone's delay can go and I think it's <BR>
16 if I recall a post by Baelish on this matter.  This is<BR>
why lots of folks think stuff doesn't stack - the<BR>
player is just bumping up into the haste &quot;floor&quot;. <BR>
Baelish (I think it was Baelish hehe maybe GZ even)<BR>
pointed out how many tanks with haste weaps are just<BR>
as fast with lower level speed buffs than the level <BR>
49 ench spell SLW because of the cap.  In other words,<BR>
you can use multiple things to speed you up, but there's<BR>
only so fast you're gonna go. <BR>
<BR>

				</font>
