	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just to let everyone know.. I want to make sure this is clear.<BR>
<BR>
Haste items do not stack with other haste items.<BR>
<BR>
So if you have a berserker cloak and a FBSS. The higher haste % will kick in. I believe it's the berserker cloak.<BR>
<BR>
Haste items do stack with haste spells.<BR>
<BR>
FBSS and enchanter haste spell. (If they do have one)<BR>
<BR>
Haste items do stack with haste spells and haste songs.<BR>
<BR>
FBSS, Haste spell, Anthem De Arms (bard song).<BR>
<BR>
Haste spells do not stack on eachother. So the shaman that tries to haste you can't haste if the enchanter already did.<BR>
<BR>
Good clear... thanks for listening.<BR>
<BR>
Magitech Bioblast
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
