	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Source: Everquest Gameplay Forum.<BR>
<BR>
The deal with haste-items and haste-spells: <BR>
<BR>
1. There is a hard cap on how much someone can be hasted.<BR>
<BR>
2. Haste-items can stack with haste-spells.<BR>
<BR>
3. Haste-items do have different speeds. As a rule, it's speed will basically be based off the level creature that it came from.<BR>
<BR>
4. Haste-items do not stack with other haste-items.<BR>
<BR>
5. Haste-spells do not stack with other haste spells.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
